data.description: Newer construction in the highly sought after Princess Anne Meadows community in Virginia Beach. Sitting on a 10,000+ square foot beautifully landscaped lot, this elegant home features an open floor plan with 9' ceilings on both first and second floors. Maple hardwood flooring and crown molding delight the eye throughout the first floor. Love to cook? This dream of a  kitchen features a huge island, professional series appliances, quartz countertops and a custom backsplash. Come snuggle up in front of the fire place in the cozy living room. Or have coffee in the bright and airy sunroom that overlooks the in-ground pool and patio. Lovely hardwood stairs lead to the second and third floors. The second floor features the bedrooms, which are large and have plenty of closet space, the loft and the utility room. Who doesn't love having a utility room near the bedrooms? The primary bedroom boasts a luxurious ensuite bath with marble floors, a shower and soaking tub, as well as a large walk-in closet. A full third floor unfinished attic has more than ample room for storage. Step inside and imagine yourself living in the dream!
